@* =============================================================
   FuriousRhinoLogo.razor
   Inline SVG logo component. Renders the full rounded-square
   logo by default, or a circle-clipped variant via CircleVariant.

   Parameters:
     Size          — width/height in px (default 48)
     CircleVariant — true = clip to circle, hide the rect border
     CssClass      — extra CSS classes on the <svg> element
     AriaLabel     — accessible label (default "Furious Rhino logo")
   ============================================================= *@

